{"tid":906882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第四型人格","createTime":"2018-11-18T10:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T14:11:04.000Z","uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90c2eb6c0b0e5a4fd7a4aba8bbab5ac9b444e6fd","tid":906882,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:53:40.000Z","msg":"一、形成性格的背景<br />\n普遍有被遺棄的經歷，總是帶著憂郁感，核心問題是缺失感和時常降低的自尊<br />\n在悲情浪漫者的成長經歷中，總是有被拋棄或者類似的經歷，或是父母離異，他們長期失去父愛或母愛；或是父母其中一方在他們生活中時而出現時而消失，他們因此而感到悲傷<br />\n在他們成年後，這種遺缺感也不會消失。他們因此若有所失，總是帶著憂郁感<br />\n <br />\n有冇ching都係呢個人格?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cb5687cdb247547c7a2766d097ed3da5c4b4bd","tid":906882,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"不gay嘅藝術家"},{"pid":"cc0d7ebaa3ccd80517b06b9aa04e557496f75788","tid":906882,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8cb5687cdb247547c7a2766d097ed3da5c4b4bd","tid":906882,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"不gay嘅藝術家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:59:59.000Z","msg":"hi 你好"},{"pid":"5fc3831a79259bbbadd6d18c96a53da9aed31e2b","tid":906882,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T14:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}